<https://egdc-frontend.vercel.app/case-studies/10> dcterms:title "Integrated Operations Center (IOC) for Nicosia"@en ;
	dcterms:description "The Integrated Operations Center platform is a digital enablement platform that increases productivity, efficiency and growth through agile introduction and largely automated utilization of digital operational technology assets and capabilities."@en ;
